These are Puzzles for 3x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-1::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: classical, house, pop
There are 3 different nationalities: indian, thai, turkish
The people use 3 different means of transport: taxi, skateboard, boat
1. the person driving the boat is in an even position##4
2. the thai is on the left of the indian##1
3. the fan of classical is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1
4. the thai is in an even position##4
5. the fan of pop is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |    3     |
| Music-Genre   | pop       | classical     | house    |
| Nationality   | turkish   | thai          | indian   |
| Transport         | taxi | boat | skateboard |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-2::.
There 3 different types of food: avocado, cabbage, nectarine
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: action, disaster, superhero
The people have 3 different jobs:  dancer, musician, teacher
1. the teacher is the person eating nectarine##1
2. the person watching superhero movies is on the left or right of the teacher##3
3. the person eating nectarine is on the left of the person eating cabbage##1
4. the musician is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
5. the teacher is in an even position##4
6. the teacher is on the right of the person watching superhero movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2      |    3     |
| Food    | avocado     | nectarine  | cabbage  |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero | disaster | action    |
| Job     | dancer      | teacher    | musician |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-3::.
House: farmhouse, cottage, wooden
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: funk, hip-hop, reggae
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: lacrosse, skiing, weightlifting
1. the person who's sport is lacrosse is in an even position##4
2. the person who's sport is weightlifting is the farmhouse house##1
3. the fan of reggae is on the right of the fan of funk##1
4. the wooden house is on the right of the farmhouse house##1
5. the wooden house is on the left or right of the fan of reggae##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |   3    |
| House          | farmhouse         | wooden     | cottage   |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop       | funk     | reggae |
| Sport         | weightlifting | lacrosse | skiing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-4::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: coffee, hot-chocolate, mirinda
The people have 3 different hobbies: puzzles, skydiving, sudoku
3 different pets are kept: ferret, goldfish, snake
1. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
2. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
3. the person who's hobby is puzzles is in an odd position##4
4. the person drinking coffee is on the far left##1
5. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2     |       3       |
| Beverage   | coffee | mirinda  | hot-chocolate |
| Hobby        | sudoku | skydiving  | puzzles |
| Pet        | ferret | goldfish | snake         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-5::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: romance, satire, time-travel
There are 3 different nationalities: american, australian, chinese
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: siglo, bolivar, alhambra
1. the american is on the left or right of the siglo-smoker##3
2. the australian is on the left of the alhambra-smoker##1
3. the siglo-smoker is on the right of the person watching romance movies##1
4. the siglo-smoker is in an odd position##4
5. the person watching time-travel movies is on the far left##1
6. the person watching satire movies is on the left or right of the person watching romance movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |    3    |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel | romance  | satire  |
| Nationality   | australian  | american | chinese |
| Cigar           | bolivar  | alhambra    | siglo    |

