.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-6::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: cola, milk, sprite
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: d&b, reggae, disco
The people use 3 different means of transport: boat, car, quad-bike
1. the person drinking cola is between the person driving the quad-bike and the fan of disco##2
2. the fan of d&b is the person drinking milk##1
3. the person drinking cola is on the left of the fan of d&b##1
4. the person driving the car is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |   2   |      3      |
| Beverage    | sprite  | cola  | milk        |
| Music-Genre       | disco | reggae | d&b |
| Transport   | boat    | car   | quad-bike   |

