.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-8::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: sports, comedy, superhero
The people have 3 different jobs:  musician, photographer, pilot
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: lacrosse, skiing, tennis
1. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the person watching sports movies##1
2. the person who's sport is lacrosse is between the pilot and the person watching superhero movies##2
3. the photographer is on the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
4. the person watching superhero movies is in an odd position##4
5. the person who's sport is tennis is the person watching superhero movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2     |      3       |
| Movie-Genre    | sports   | comedy | superhero       |
| Job     | pilot  | musician  | photographer |
| Sport   | skiing | lacrosse  | tennis       |

