.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-13::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: 7up, hot-chocolate, sprite
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: basketball, golf, water-polo
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: fantasy, scientific, thriller
1. the person watching fantasy movies is on the far right##1
2. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left or right of the person who's sport is golf##3
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is in an even position##4
4. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
5. the person watching thriller movies is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |       2       |     3      |
| Beverage    | 7up        | hot-chocolate | sprite     |
| Sport       | basketball | golf          | water-polo |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific     | thriller          | fantasy       |

