.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-14::.
There 3 different types of food: apple, artichoke, grapefruit
3 different games are played: domino, billiard, monopoly
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: country, disco, pop
1. the fan of disco is on the left of the person eating artichoke##1
2. the fan of disco is in an odd position##4
3. the person playing monopoly is on the left of the person eating grapefruit##1
4. the fan of country is on the right of the fan of disco##1
5. the person playing billiard is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person eating artichoke is on the right of the person playing domino##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2     |     3      |
| Food          | apple | artichoke | grapefruit |
| Game           | domino | monopoly   | billiard  |
| Music-Genre   | disco | country   | pop        |

