3. the owner of the pony is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
4. the person eating tomato is the fan of r&b##1
5. the person eating eggplant is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |   3    |
| Food   | tomato      | eggplant | asparagus |
| Music-Genre   | r&b        | punk         | trance |
| Pet           | chinchilla | pony         | frog   |

