3. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the person driving the boat##1
4. the person driving the boat is on the left of the musician##1
5. the electrician is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
6. the person who's hobby is hiking is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
