1. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the far left##1
2. the paramedic is in an even position##4
3. the social-worker is on the right of the person who's sport is climbing##1
4. the pilot is the canadian##1
5. the thai is on the right of the german##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2     |       3       |
| Job     | pilot      | paramedic | social-worker |
| Nationality     | canadian | german      | thai           |
| Sport   | water-polo | climbing  | volleyball    |

